    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>LOPEZ CLOSER TO EXTRADITION</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Benjamin Jones</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Jones, Benjamin</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Spanish prosecutors give preliminary approval for former General Motors Corp executive Jose Ignacio Lopez de Arriortua to be extradited to US, where he is wanted on charges of stealing company secrets; Lopez is to appear in court July 7 to state whether he will fight extradition (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Spanish prosecutors have given preliminary approval for the former General Motors executive Jose Ignacio Lopez de Arriortua to be extradited to the United States, where he is wanted on charges of stealing company secrets. Mr. Lopez is to appear in court tomorrow to state whether he will fight the extradition. He was indicted in May by a federal grand jury in Detroit.</p>
        <p>Benjamin Jones (NYT)</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
